      <scopecontent id="aspace_2ca88dc939e76ca9f60c9b635877d2de">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of minutes and tax and statistics books documenting the operations and activities of the New Haven County Medical Association, which formed in 1784 as the Medical Society of New-Haven County.</p>  
